{"tid":914294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小巴輾女童手　十途人抬車救出","createTime":"2018-11-24T06:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T08:34:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c2efb6d5f7f02988c61d8ea891551d8484f35a11","tid":914294,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181124/20553520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F20553520&d=64iNwou4P6kIin4d5GQDBsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3e87a3dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F20553520&h=7dce995f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181124/20553520</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月24日 <br />\n<br />\n小巴輾女童手　十途人抬車救出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181124/large/24la5p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181124%2Flarge%2F24la5p3.jpg&h=10ac52c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名途人合力抬起小巴，將壓在輪下的女童救出。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名4歲女童昨早乘坐小巴上學，落車時意外被車輪輾過左手且壓於車底，情況危急，幸得十多名熱心途人合力抬起車尾，將女童救出送院，目前情況穩定，警方正調查意外起因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181124/large/24la5p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181124%2Flarge%2F24la5p4.jpg&h=1a695bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受傷女童事後送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n書包留車內　父拍門車照開<br />\n<br />\n現場位於土瓜灣馬頭涌道，昨早9時許，一部專線小巴沿上址往九龍城方向行駛，至135號聖公會聖三一堂對開停車，據知一名4歲姓黃的幼稚園女生，由父親接送上學，黃父與女童下車後發現忘記拿走書包，轉身拍門叫喚司機停車，但44歲姓林司機未有為意如常開行，結果身形矮小的女童先被小巴撞到右腳，失衡倒地後左手被車輛輾過壓住，痛極哭喊。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者表示，當時女童的手掌被壓於車輪下，無法動彈，熱心途人獲悉後號召十多人一起抬起車尾，成功拔出女童左手，「好緊張呀！其他人一擁而上，有男有女，合力成功將女童救出。當時妹妹按住隻手，喊得好犀利！」救護車接報到場安排女童送院，經治理後情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n警方封鎖涉事路段調查，向司機及女童父親查問，現正調查意外起因涉及駕駛盲點抑或有人不小心駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張培生  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n曾有男女同志為公屋「結婚」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n受保護物種命運迥異 犀角拍賣叫停　沉香招客競投"},{"pid":"12d6bdfbdf007c6414cefe8db7a9e157fce9ff8b","tid":914294,"uid":40272,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"細路個樣咁冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6944bafafd00a2141217e0b8f2bd5fa2ce91c51","tid":914294,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T07:45:38.000Z","msg":"我俾門夾到都痛到暈咗 個妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0b58da28f10be72382e0a9ab7e2e233bfa3671","tid":914294,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6944bafafd00a2141217e0b8f2bd5fa2ce91c51","tid":914294,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T07:45:38.000Z","msg":"我俾門夾到都痛到暈咗 個妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208682309879a87577ab933d097f93a12571e1df","tid":914294,"uid":117509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:30:24.000Z","msg":"佢個樣真係唔似比車車過隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f42e4c1e25828e6249389c25a840d922e1d5c1","tid":914294,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:34:04.000Z","msg":"條妹差少少就變支那治癒gif主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個老豆都唔知點睇住個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}